        <h1>Welcome to the Torrenting Education Site</h1>
        <h2>What is Torrenting?</h2>
        <p>Torrenting is a method of file sharing that allows users to download files from multiple sources simultaneously. It's commonly used for sharing large files such as movies, music, and software.</p>
        
        <h2>How Does Torrenting Work?</h2>
        <p>Torrenting works using a protocol called BitTorrent. Users download and upload pieces of files to and from each other, forming a network of file sharing.</p>
        
